AngloGold Ashanti Argentine Mine Closed Due to Strike, Opi Says

-- B y   R o d r i g o   O r i h u e l a
-- 
2011-06-15T16:52:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-15/anglogold-ashanti-argentine-mine-closed-due-to-strike-opi-says.html
AngloGold Ashanti Ltd. (ANG) ’s Argentine
unit, Cerro Vanguardia, has been closed since yesterday because
of a workers’ strike,  news website Opi Santa Cruz  reported,
citing Javier Castro, a union official.  Workers want the company to pay a bonus for production and
to reopen salary talks, Castro said, according to Opi.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rodrigo Orihuela in Buenos Aires at 
 rorihuela@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at 
 dcrofts@bloomberg.net  